    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately deferred as not-assessed per the MRL 2 assessment plan. The primary validation result demonstrates RH < 1 at all five operating points with maximum deviation of 12% against reference data. The assessment team concluded that the CFD model provides sufficient credibility for the intended CPB hemolysis COU. Note: the primary validation activity employed high-fidelity numerical simulation rather than direct experimental measurement; the team asserted this is functionally equivalent for MRL 2 purposes, a position accepted by the credibility assessment lead.",
